236
00:17:45,015 --> 00:17:46,777
So there'll be discussions about that.

237
00:17:47,438 --> 00:17:51,002
Overall, I would just encourage residents strongly to follow these meetings.

238
00:17:51,503 --> 00:17:51,904
Go to them.

