00:17:53,412 --> 00:18:03,980
advertise them on my social media page, but just follow them, go, make a public comment, and keep up to date because the decision of what we do with this high school, it's really gonna impact the community in a lot of different ways.

240
00:18:04,361 --> 00:18:13,628
Quality of education, our ability to financially do well in the city, and a lot of other things as well.

