245
00:18:45,277 --> 00:18:48,880
I don't know what's going to happen, but it's interesting.

246
00:18:48,940 --> 00:18:50,642
It's an interesting thing to follow.

247
00:18:50,742 --> 00:19:00,990
And, I mean, if you live in Method, you're a homeowner, you pay rent, whatever, I would advise people to get involved.

248
00:19:01,030 --> 00:19:01,491
You're right.

249
00:19:01,891 --> 00:19:02,511
That's the key.

250
00:19:03,592 --> 00:19:05,033
Know what's going on in the city.

251
00:19:06,094 --> 00:19:07,896
So I want to thank you for all that.

