00:19:29,964 --> 00:19:39,887
We know in January 2026, the city council restarted zoning initiative, and I know you're following that.

257
00:19:43,028 --> 00:19:44,508
Following it really good.

258
00:19:46,049 --> 00:19:47,410
You know what you're talking about.

